Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: California's sea otters
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xp7x
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Nov 1985
Not extinct, just hiding - California's sea otters return to their native waters. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.